<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Thank You — Sites by Mel</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <style>
    body { background: #f4f1ec; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; }
    .thanks-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 56px 48px; text-align: center; max-width: 520px; }
    .check { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    p { color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; font-size: .92rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="thanks-card">
  <div class="check">🎉</div>
  <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px">Sites by <span style="color:var(--gold)">Mel</span></div>
  <h1>You're all set, <%= business_name %>!</h1>
  <p>Your intake form has been received. I'll review everything and reach out within <strong>1–2 business days</strong> with an update on your site.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:16px">In the meantime, feel free to reply to your welcome email if you think of anything else. I personally read every message.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:24px;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600">— Mel</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
